No. D-2719. In the Matter of Discipline of Gregory Bartko. 565 U.S. 1054, 132 S. Ct. 812,

181 L. Ed. 2d 522,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8399. November 28, 2011.

Gregory Bartko, of Atlanta, Georgia, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
